The Managing Director of the National lnland Waterways Authority (NIWA), Dr. George N. Moghalu, has described Vice President Yemi Osinbajo as a dependable Vice Captain of President Muhammadu Buhari’s administration. Moghalu while celebrating Osinbajo at 63, prayed for continued guidance of the Vice presidet I the discharge of his duties. In a statement, Wednesday in Abuja, the NIWA boss who called for emulation of VP Yemi Osinbajo’s traits, said through him the administration has recorded giant strides in the last five years. “I felicitate with our amiable and very hardworking Vice President, Prof. Yemi Osibanjo GCFR on the occasion of his 63rd birthday celebration. “As a highly dependable Vice Captain of the President Muhammadu Buhari led APC Administration, which has recorded giant strides in the last five years,  I and my family celebrate you. “As you mark yet another milestone in your life, l would like to wish you well and pray that God continues to guide every of your footsteps,” Moghalu stated.